'''Sagebrush Corporation''' is a publishing company that republishes many ''[[Star Wars]]'' books for younger readers. Demco Media's Turtleback books were acquired by Sagebrush on [[March 1]], [[2006]].<ref name="Sagebrush">{{WebCite|url=http://www.story-house.com/webprd_media/pdf/sagebrush_pr.pdf|text="Sagebrush Corporation Acquires Turtleback<sup>®</sup> Books from Demco Media" press release|archivedate=20060327162423|nolive=1}}</ref>

On [[July 26]], [[2006]], Follett Software Company acquired the Sagebrush Corporation.<ref name="Follett">{{WebCite|url=http://www.fsc.follett.com/newsnevents/pressreleases/release.cfm?pressID=25|text=Follett Acquires Sagebrush Corporation's Library Automation Business|archivedate=20060818091626|nolive=1}}</ref>

